                <h2 class="h6 text-center"><a>Target Discovery Core (TDC)</a></h2>
                <p>The mission of the TDC is to provide researchers at UT Health San Antonio (UTHSA) and other Texas-based institutes with cutting-edge target identification and validation (TIV) technologies, advancing fundamental cancer biology research and accelerating the discovery of cancer therapeutics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-2">
