                <h2 class="h6 text-center"><a>Greehey CCRI Xenograft & Cell-Lines Core</a></h2>
                <p>The Xenograft and Cell Lines Core at Greehey CCRI offers preclinical testing of chemotherapeutics and drug combinations in mouse models. This service is available to the UT Health San Antonio research community, pharmaceutical companies, and any lab interested in conducting animal research.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cell small-12 medium-2">
                <img class="margin-bottom" src="../../images/gccri/GPPB.jpg">
